OL,3,CGuernsey's top committee announce new
OL,4,Cfunding plan for education project
OL,6,FThe first stage includes completing
OL,7,FThe Guernsey Institute at Les Ozouets
OL,8,Fand will be funded by borrowing #55
OL,9,Fmillion, using #33 million from the
OL,10,Fisland's reserves and any money made
OL,11,Ffrom selling land at the Coutanchez
OL,12,Fcampus.
OL,14,FIt means the sixth-form centre and the
OL,15,Fsports facilities will not move
OL,16,Fforward initially.
