OL,3,CGuernsey's top committee announce new
OL,4,Cfunding plan for education project
OL,6,FThe committee's president, Deputy
OL,7,FLyndon Trott said: "We can't continue
OL,8,Fwith the uncertainty around Post-16
OL,9,Feducation, and from the outset of our
OL,10,Fshort time on the Policy & Resources
OL,11,FCommittee, we felt finding a
OL,12,Fcompromise is an urgent priority.
OL,14,F"This comes against a backdrop of
OL,15,Fbetter-than-expected economic growth
OL,16,Fin Guernsey over the past two years,
OL,17,Fputting the island in a stronger
OL,18,Fposition both to fund borrowing and to
OL,19,Freplenish its reserves."
