OL,3,CGuernsey's top committee announce new
OL,4,Cfunding plan for education project
OL,6,FThe assembly has already approved the
OL,7,Fmodel for secondary and post-16
OL,8,Feducation but has never .
OL,10,FIf the amendment for this first phase
OL,11,Fis approved then the States would be
OL,12,Fgiven the option to proceed with the
OL,13,Fconstruction of foundations for the
OL,14,Fnew Sixth Form Centre, also at Les
OL,15,FOzouets.
OL,17,FThe new proposals will be presented as
OL,18,Fan amendment to the States at this
OL,19,Fweek's Government Work Plan debate.
