OL,3,CGuernsey's top committee announce new
OL,4,Cfunding plan for education project
OL,6,FPresident of the Committee for
OL,7,FEducation, Sport & Culture, Deputy
OL,8,FAndrea Dudley-Owen said: "I welcome
OL,9,Fthe Policy & Resources Committee's
OL,10,Fengagement to find a way to deliver
OL,11,Fthe new Les Ozouets Campus.
OL,13,F"Although I am disappointed that a way
OL,14,Fto deliver the entire site has not
OL,15,Fbeen found at this time, I am grateful
OL,16,Fto the Policy & Resources Committee
OL,17,Ffor their option to lay the
OL,18,Ffoundations for the Sixth Form block."
